<title>USA: Russ Berrie eyes options for toy units.</title>
<headline>Russ Berrie eyes options for toy units.</headline>
<dateline>OAKLAND, N.J. 1996-12-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Russ Berrie and Co said on Monday it engaged Schroder Wertheim &amp; Co Inc to explore strategic options for its toy subsidiaries -- Cap Toys Inc and OddzOn Products Inc.</p>
<p>These units design and market toys to retail stores in the United States and worldwide.</p>
<p>The company said the move was consistent with its strategy to maximize shareholder value.</p>
